reviews.title: Bagel boy Amsterdam
reviews.text:
Absolutely incredible food. A nice and small menu but excellent combos to choose from. 
Food was 10/10 and the atmosphere was brilliant, loved it. 

Staff were excellent and very customer friendly.

reviews.title: Delicious bagels for an early lunch
reviews.text: I've tried a simple bagel. There aren't fully vegan options on the menu, but the staff suggested right away the avocado bagel without the cheese. Although it had just a few ingredients it was really good! The bagel dough is flufy and savoury - I really enjoyed it. And I think it has a fair price for most of the prices practiced in that area.

reviews.title: Fresh & delicious!
reviews.text: Absolutely delicious bagel! Very attentive, kind staff and I could eat this bagel over and over again. Fresh and so tasty! Not too expensive either, considering the location and how expensive other foods are. Must visit!

reviews.title: Poor service, good bagels
reviews.text:
Went to get some brunch on the go.
I ordered an everything bagel with cream cheese and added avocado, egg: 1€ each. 
Cheap and delicious. 

However, I got American cheese added by mistake, which I didn’t like … and very poor service. 
I had ordered, then a group of 5 came inside and ordered. I waited then ~20 min for my order (mind you, only so few ingredients…).
The employee made ALL other orders, then mine for last… even though I ordered first? I made notice of this before he would continue with the rest, but still continued to finish the group order 🤯
I got a bit hangry, I mean if I commented on it with dissatisfaction, then why would you not try to fix your mistake…? 

Would recommend for the taste, but not for the overall experience.

reviews.title: Good bagels but disappointing service
reviews.text:
Dear Bagel boy,

I normally enjoy your bagels, but unfortunately I recently had a less than good experience. Last week I ordered a bagel without bacon because of my allergy, but on the way home I discovered that it had bacon on it anyway. On my next visit I mentioned this, but no apology was offered or a solution was offered. There was a neutral facial expression, as if it were a normal course of action by a blonde English speaking lady.

I hope that more attention will be paid to such requests in the future.

review.title: Goede bagels, maar teleurstellende service
review.text:
Beste Bagel boy,

Ik geniet normaal gesproken van jullie bagels, maar helaas heb ik recent een minder goede ervaring gehad. Vorige week bestelde ik een bagel zonder bacon vanwege mijn allergie, maar onderweg naar huis ontdekte ik voor mijn hap dat er toch bacon op zat. Bij mijn volgende bezoek heb ik dit vermeld, maar er werd geen excuses aangeboden of een oplossing geboden. Er werd met een neutrale gezichtsuitdrukking gereageerd, alsof het een normale gang van zaken is door een blonde engels sprekende dame.

Ik hoop dat er in de toekomst meer aandacht wordt besteed aan dergelijke verzoeken.
